{"tid":279631,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"嚴選全港最垃圾麥當勞","createTime":"2017-06-11T12:07:45.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-13T04:10:15.000Z","uid":82097,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"301bc2f03306a9a160195e4bbc67fb8e0f409aa4","tid":279631,"uid":82097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T12:07:45.000Z","msg":"朗豪坊個間真係首屈一指<br />\n一到星期六日食晒屎咁<br />\n個部機禁就快啦 d野食等到佛誕都未出 <br />\n前台得一個人處理d單嗌餐號都夠膽死<br />\n仲要擺到明係暑期工d妹妹仔唔知自己做緊乜<br />\n個魂遊到外太空真係想係佢耳邊大叫醒未啊<br />\n後面班友走來走去望住部機又係唔知乜事<br />\n個bar台已經夠多食物d雪糕都融到變水好心就幫下條女啦<br />\n等到終於有餐夠膽死可以俾少個包<br />\n變相又要等過 仲要有時急起上黎無睇就走左真係無仇報<br />\n又多蝗蟲帶埋d蝗子蝗孫係度跑來跑去<br />\n撞親佢除左抵啦都唔知講咩好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n真心覺得以前一個人負責點餐一個負責執有效率好多"},{"pid":"e88b82fb815167fc9d9445fb66fcc8c243bf0496","tid":279631,"uid":51978,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T12:09:52.000Z","msg":"食垃圾老麥咁屄多要求 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n垃圾就垃圾 間間都係垃圾"},{"pid":"a342b3a8f9b68616833360c1811f015a163f7d40","tid":279631,"uid":21758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T20:22:47.000Z","msg":"屯門蝴蝶村個間<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba48e41add4926d22235beeb35675c3b429fae56","tid":279631,"uid":27664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T20:28:05.000Z","msg":"現在係成班人等住餐望住d on9，心裏面應該諗：得未呀，少少野都要咁耐"},{"pid":"7bf295fb496510b88af093566cc55926fd149963","tid":279631,"uid":97668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T20:29:52.000Z","msg":"始創對面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 夜晚臭到"},{"pid":"553d62eecb7c111e5b9660e801c3e610ea02204e","tid":279631,"uid":2506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T21:38:58.000Z","msg":"粉嶺聯和墟先係最差<img